    <item>
      <title>奥尔班助手在第一天就暗示乌克兰投降，引发强烈抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/orban-aide-sparks-outcry-suggesting-ukraine-surrender-from-day-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班的一名高级助手称乌克兰抵御俄罗斯入侵的决定“不负责任”，并暗示匈牙利不会拿起武器，此举在国内引发强烈抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/orban-aide-sparks-outcry-suggesting-ukraine-surrender-from-day-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 13:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非首都市长因联盟政府垮台被罢免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/mayor-of-south-africa-s-capital-ousted-as-coalition-collapses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政南非首都的多党联盟垮台后，该市市长于周四被罢免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/mayor-of-south-africa-s-capital-ousted-as-coalition-collapses</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:58:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市考虑将出租车保险金额削减 75% 至 5 万美元以援助司机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-weighs-slashing-cab-insurance-75-to-50-000-to-aid-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市议会将于本周提出一项法案，大幅减少出租车和共享乘车车辆必须维持的保险金额，以期控制该市最大出租车保险公司破产可能带来的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-weighs-slashing-cab-insurance-75-to-50-000-to-aid-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:23:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国加入美国行列，对俄罗斯“暗黑舰队”旗下的液化天然气船舶实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/uk-joins-us-in-sanctioning-lng-ships-linked-to-russia-dark-fleet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国已对与俄罗斯液化天然气出口有关的五艘船只和两家实体实施制裁，其中包括据信在其北极地区最新出口设施装货的油轮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/uk-joins-us-in-sanctioning-lng-ships-linked-to-russia-dark-fleet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港编辑因首起媒体煽动案被判入狱 21 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/hong-kong-editor-jailed-21-months-in-first-media-sedition-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港法院以发表有关民主活动人士的文章为由判处一名前编辑 21 个月监禁，这是香港回归中国以来第一名因煽动叛乱罪而入狱的记者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/hong-kong-editor-jailed-21-months-in-first-media-sedition-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求还清每天高达 11.2 万美元的最大债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-seeks-to-wipe-out-his-biggest-debt-costing-112-000-a-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师正在执行一项任务，即消除他最大的财务负担——一项近 5 亿美元的欺诈判决，该判决的金额每天飙升约 10 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-seeks-to-wipe-out-his-biggest-debt-costing-112-000-a-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡访问联合国，从战争走向外交敌对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前，本雅明·内塔尼亚胡来到联合国，宣扬阿拉伯世界和平的祝福。他回来时，该地区正处于全面战争的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自 2007 年以来法国债务风险首次高于西班牙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-s-bond-yield-surpasses-spain-s-for-first-time-since-2007</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2007 年以来，法国债券首次被认为比西班牙债券风险更高，这一象征性的逆转凸显了法国金融市场困境的严重程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-s-bond-yield-surpasses-spain-s-for-first-time-since-2007</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯在联邦腐败调查后被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-adams-indicted-after-federal-corruption-probe-nyt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 在接受联邦腐败调查后已被起诉，这使得这位美国最大城市市长的政治前途受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-adams-indicted-after-federal-corruption-probe-nyt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯呼吁美国提供关键矿产储备和税收抵免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-vows-to-create-us-critical-minerals-stockpile-incentives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯誓言要建立国家关键矿产储备，她表示，从电池到国防系统等各个领域所使用的材料对于经济和国家安全都是必需的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-vows-to-create-us-critical-minerals-stockpile-incentives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:17:17 GMT</pubDate>
